title: New Zealand v Australia: Live scores, stats and commentary
text:
Commentary 
New Zealand leads the three-match series 1-0 after almost throwing away a winning position in the opening match after Marcus Stoinis' other-worldly heroics. 
The second match was a farcical washout, with the Napier outfield refusing to dry despite little rain throughout the matchday. 
Follow all the action with our live stats, scores and commentary. Live scorecard
